                                smaller image), it is often faster to convert a raw image to qcow2 and upload it than to
                                upload the raw file.</para>
                        </note>
                    </listitem>
                </varlistentry>
                <varlistentry>
                    <term><emphasis role="bold">aki</emphasis></term>
